Package: RecView
Type: Package
Title: View and Locate Recombination Positions Using Pedigree Data
Version: 1.1.0-1
Author: Hongkai Zhang
Maintainer: Hongkai Zhang <hongkai.zhang@biol.lu.se>
Description: The package is designed to distribute the "RecView" ShinyApp which aims at providing a user-friendly GUI for viewing and locating recombination positions on chromosomes recombination positions using pedigree data.
